.TH midb_agent 4gx "" "Gromox" "Gromox admin reference"
.SH Synopsis
.PP
midb_agent \(em midb(8gx) connector for smtp(8gx), imap(8gx), pop3(8gx)
.SH Configuration file directives
.SS connection_num
.PP
The number of connections to keep open towards midb(8gx).
.PP
Default: \fI5\fP
.SS context_average_mem
.PP
Enables and sets the size of a memory pool (in object count; the actual size is
256 bytes * context_num * context_average_mem). imap(8gx) and pop3(8gx) require
this to be non-zero for full functionality.
.PP
Default: \fI1024\fP
.SH Files
.PP
\fIdata_file_path\fP/midb_list.txt: midb multiserver map
.SH See also
.PP
\fBgromox\fP(7)
